Feature: City Management

  Scenario: City structure and buildings 
    Given player enters any city
    When they explore city layout
    Then they should find at least 8 building types
    And each building should have specific functions
    And city should have unique architectural style
    And buildings should be logically arranged

  Scenario: City economy and population 
    Given player visits different cities
    When they observe city characteristics
    Then each city should have distinct economy type
    And population should affect shop availability
    And city wealth should influence item prices
    And cities should have cultural uniqueness

  Scenario: City services and facilities 
    Given player needs city services
    When they seek assistance
    Then they should find inns for rest
    And they should find training grounds
    And they should find quest boards
    And they should find crafting stations

  Scenario: City discovery and information 
    Given player discovers new city
    When they enter city for first time
    Then they should receive city description
      ASSERT FAILED: Description should mention city characteristics

    And they should learn about available services
    And they should see population size
    And they should understand economic focus

  Scenario: City reputation system 
    Given player interacts with city over time
    When they complete quests or trade
    Then their reputation should change
    And reputation should affect prices
    And reputation should unlock new services
    And high reputation should provide special benefits
      ASSERT FAILED: Positive reputation should provide benefits


